@startuml UC-06_View_Analytics

title UC-06: View Usage Analytics - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #F57C00
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant AnalyticsService
participant Database as DB

User -> Frontend: 1. Click Analytics Dashboard
Frontend -> API: 2. GET /api/v1/analytics/dashboard?period=month
API -> AnalyticsService: 3. get_dashboard_overview(user_id, period)
AnalyticsService -> DB: 4. Query analytics events
DB --> AnalyticsService: 5. Events data
AnalyticsService -> DB: 6. Calculate metrics (aggregation)
DB --> AnalyticsService: 7. Aggregated data
AnalyticsService -> AnalyticsService: 8. Process & format data
AnalyticsService --> API: 9. Return {workflow_metrics, execution_stats, ...}
API --> Frontend: 10. 200 OK + dashboard data
Frontend --> User: 11. Display charts & metrics

@enduml
